      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... that's a really heavy way to put it. \"A source of darkness.\" It's just true though. Every time I look at them, I just see them losing their childhood because they're too busy worrying about me or cleaning up my emotional messes. I'm just a weight around their necks. It feels like the more I try to help, the more I'm actually just hurting them.",
